I was on when this was happening. I tried to get the person to ask the name of a long lost character you know of mine <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
I figured it be a pretty sure way to determine if it was you.<br>
Guess they didn't try or whatever, I never found out what happened in the end.  But you do have to watch out, there is those that will try anything to scam you.  With the unknown face behind the keys these losers have no guilt or conscience of what they do.  Be careful out there.<br>
-Jen<br>
